<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="he" dir="rtl">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>מזל טוב קרן לביא - יום הולדת 50</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Frank+Ruhl+Libre:wght@300;400;500;700;900&family=Heebo:wght@300;400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --gold: #C9A84C; --gold-light: #F0D080; --gold-dark: #8B6914;
  --bg-deep: #0A0A0F; --rose: #C84B6E; --rose-light: #E8698A;
  --cream: #F5EDD8; --text-muted: #8888AA;
  --shadow-gold: rgba(201,168,76,0.3); --shadow-rose: rgba(200,75,110,0.25);
  --card-front: linear-gradient(135deg,#1A1A2E 0%,#16213E 50%,#0F3460 100%);
  --card-back: linear-gradient(135deg,#2D1B4E 0%,#4A1942 50%,#6B1F3A 100%);
}
*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
body{background:var(--bg-deep);font-family:'Heebo',sans-serif;color:var(--cream);min-height:100vh;overflow-x:hidden}
body::before{content:'';position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;
  background-image:
    radial-gradient(1px 1px at 10% 15%,rgba(255,255,255,.6) 0%,transparent 100%),
    radial-gradient(1px 1px at 25% 40%,rgba(255,255,255,.4) 0%,transparent 100%),
    radial-gradient(1.5px 1.5px at 50% 10%,rgba(201,168,76,.5) 0%,transparent 100%),
    radial-gradient(1px 1px at 70% 60%,rgba(255,255,255,.5) 0%,transparent 100%),
    radial-gradient(1px 1px at 85% 25%,rgba(255,255,255,.3) 0%,transparent 100%),
    radial-gradient(1.5px 1.5px at 35% 75%,rgba(201,168,76,.4) 0%,transparent 100%),
    radial-gradient(1px 1px at 60% 85%,rgba(255,255,255,.4) 0%,transparent 100%),
    radial-gradient(1px 1px at 5% 55%,rgba(255,255,255,.3) 0%,transparent 100%),
    radial-gradient(1.5px 1.5px at 45% 30%,rgba(200,75,110,.4) 0%,transparent 100%);
  pointer-events:none;z-index:0}
.app{position:relative;z-index:1;padding:0 0 60px}

/* ── HEADER ── */
.header{text-align:center;padding:48px 20px 28px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;transition:padding .4s}
.header::before{content:’’;position:absolute;top:-100px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);
width:600px;height:600px;background:radial-gradient(ellipse,rgba(201,168,76,.08) 0%,transparent 70%);pointer-events:none}
.header-deco{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:18px;margin-bottom:14px}
.deco-line{height:1px;width:120px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,var(–gold),transparent)}
.deco-diamond{width:10px;height:10px;background:var(–gold);transform:rotate(45deg);box-shadow:0 0 12px var(–gold)}
.header h1{font-family:‘Frank Ruhl Libre’,serif;font-size:clamp(1.8rem,4vw,3.4rem);font-weight:900;line-height:1.2;
background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(–gold-light) 0%,var(–gold) 40%,var(–rose-light) 70%,var(–gold) 100%);
-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;background-clip:text;
letter-spacing:-.02em;margin-bottom:8px;transition:font-size .4s}
.header-sub{font-size:clamp(.85rem,1.5vw,1.1rem);color:var(–text-muted);font-weight:300;letter-spacing:.08em}
.sparkle-row{display:flex;justify-content:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:6px;font-size:1.1rem;opacity:.65;animation:float 3s ease-in-out infinite}
@keyframes float{0%,100%{transform:translateY(0)}50%{transform:translateY(-4px)}}

/* ── TOTAL BANNER ── */
.total-banner{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:24px;
margin:0 auto 28px;max-width:680px;padding:18px 36px;
background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(201,168,76,.08),rgba(200,75,110,.06));
border:1px solid rgba(201,168,76,.25);border-radius:16px;backdrop-filter:blur(10px);
position:relative;overflow:hidden;transition:all .4s}
.total-banner::before{content:’’;position:absolute;inset:0;
background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent 0%,rgba(201,168,76,.04) 50%,transparent 100%);
animation:shimmer 3s ease-in-out infinite}
@keyframes shimmer{0%,100%{opacity:0}50%{opacity:1}}
.total-label{font-size:.95rem;color:var(–text-muted);letter-spacing:.05em}
.total-amount{font-family:‘Frank Ruhl Libre’,serif;font-size:clamp(1.8rem,3.5vw,2.8rem);font-weight:900;
color:var(–gold-light);text-shadow:0 0 30px var(–shadow-gold);transition:all .5s;direction:ltr}
.total-amount.updated{animation:pulse-gold .5s ease}
@keyframes pulse-gold{0%{transform:scale(1)}50%{transform:scale(1.08);color:var(–rose-light)}100%{transform:scale(1)}}
.cards-count{font-size:.85rem;color:var(–text-muted);text-align:center;line-height:1.4}
.cards-count span{display:block;font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(–rose-light)}

/* ── CONTROLS ── */
.controls{display:flex;justify-content:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:26px;flex-wrap:wrap;padding:0 20px;transition:margin .4s}
.btn{padding:10px 24px;border-radius:50px;font-family:‘Heebo’,sans-serif;font-size:.9rem;font-weight:500;
cursor:pointer;transition:all .25s;border:none;letter-spacing:.02em}
.btn-tv{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(–gold-dark),var(–gold));color:#0A0A0F;box-shadow:0 4px 20px var(–shadow-gold)}
.btn-tv:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 8px 30px var(–shadow-gold)}
.btn-restore{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1A3A1A,#2E6B2E);color:#90EE90;border:1px solid rgba(100,200,100,.35);box-shadow:0 2px 12px rgba(80,160,80,.2)}
.btn-restore:hover{border-color:#90EE90;color:#fff;box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(80,200,80,.35);transform:translateY(-1px)}
.btn-reset-all{background:transparent;color:var(–text-muted);border:1px solid rgba(136,136,170,.3)}
.btn-reset-all:hover{border-color:var(–rose);color:var(–rose-light);background:rgba(200,75,110,.08)}

/* ── BOARD ── */
.board{display:grid;gap:18px;max-width:1600px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 22px;
grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(170px,1fr));transition:all .4s}

/* ── CARD ── */
.card-wrapper{perspective:1000px;height:210px;animation:card-in .4s ease both;transition:height .4s}
@keyframes card-in{from{opacity:0;transform:scale(.86) translateY(16px)}to{opacity:1;transform:scale(1) translateY(0)}}
.card-inner{position:relative;width:100%;height:100%;transform-style:preserve-3d;
transition:transform .65s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1);cursor:pointer}
.card-inner.flipped{transform:rotateY(180deg)}
.card-face{position:absolute;inset:0;backface-visibility:hidden;-webkit-backface-visibility:hidden;
border-radius:14px;overflow:hidden;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
padding:14px 12px 12px;box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.4),0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.05) inset;transition:box-shadow .3s}
.card-face:hover{box-shadow:0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.5),0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.08) inset}
.card-front{background:var(–card-front);border:1px solid rgba(201,168,76,.2)}
.card-front::before{content:’’;position:absolute;top:-30px;right:-30px;width:120px;height:120px;
background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(201,168,76,.12),transparent 70%);pointer-events:none}
.card-back{background:var(–card-back);transform:rotateY(180deg);border:1px solid rgba(200,75,110,.25)}
.card-back::before{content:’’;position:absolute;bottom:-30px;left:-30px;width:120px;height:120px;
background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(200,75,110,.12),transparent 70%);pointer-events:none}

.card-num{position:absolute;top:8px;right:10px;font-size:.65rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.22);font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.05em}
.card-value-display{font-family:‘Frank Ruhl Libre’,serif;font-size:clamp(1.5rem,2.5vw,1.9rem);font-weight:900;
color:var(–gold-light);text-shadow:0 0 20px var(–shadow-gold);line-height:1;margin:3px 0;direction:ltr;text-align:center;word-break:break-all}
.card-currency{font-size:.75rem;color:var(–gold);opacity:.7;margin-top:3px;letter-spacing:.1em;font-weight:500}
.gift-icon{font-size:1.3rem;margin-bottom:3px;filter:drop-shadow(0 0 8px var(–shadow-gold))}
.flip-hint{position:absolute;bottom:7px;right:8px;font-size:.58rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.18);letter-spacing:.05em}

/* Edit inputs */
.card-edit-input{background:rgba(255,255,255,.06);border:1px solid var(–gold);border-radius:8px;
color:var(–gold-light);font-family:‘Frank Ruhl Libre’,serif;font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:700;
width:100%;text-align:center;padding:5px 8px;outline:none;direction:ltr}
.card-edit-input:focus{border-color:var(–gold-light);box-shadow:0 0 12px var(–shadow-gold)}
.card-desc-input{background:rgba(255,255,255,.06);border:1px solid var(–rose);border-radius:8px;
color:var(–cream);font-family:‘Heebo’,sans-serif;font-size:.78rem;width:100%;text-align:center;
padding:5px 7px;outline:none;resize:none;height:55px;direction:rtl}
.card-desc-input:focus{border-color:var(–rose-light);box-shadow:0 0 12px var(–shadow-rose)}

/* Buttons inside card */
.btn-save{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(–gold-dark),var(–gold));color:#0A0A0F;border:none;
border-radius:20px;padding:4px 14px;font-size:.72rem;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;margin-top:5px;
transition:all .2s;font-family:‘Heebo’,sans-serif}
.btn-save:hover{transform:scale(1.05);box-shadow:0 4px 14px var(–shadow-gold)}
.btn-save-back{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#7B1F40,var(–rose));color:#fff}

.edit-btn{position:absolute;bottom:8px;left:8px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.06);
border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12);border-radius:50%;width:24px;height:24px;
display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;cursor:pointer;font-size:.68rem;
color:rgba(255,255,255,.38);transition:all .2s;z-index:5}
.edit-btn:hover{background:rgba(201,168,76,.15);color:var(–gold);border-color:var(–gold)}

.delete-btn{position:absolute;top:7px;left:8px;background:rgba(200,75,110,.15);
border:1px solid rgba(200,75,110,.3);border-radius:50%;width:24px;height:24px;
display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;cursor:pointer;font-size:.8rem;
color:var(–rose-light);transition:all .2s;z-index:10;line-height:1}
.delete-btn:hover{background:rgba(200,75,110,.4);border-color:var(–rose-light);transform:scale(1.15)}

.reset-one-btn{position:absolute;background:rgba(201,168,76,.1);border:1px solid rgba(201,168,76,.22);
border-radius:50%;width:24px;height:24px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
cursor:pointer;font-size:.8rem;color:rgba(201,168,76,.55);transition:all .2s;z-index:10;line-height:1}
.reset-one-btn:hover{background:rgba(201,168,76,.22);color:var(–gold-light);border-color:var(–gold);transform:scale(1.15) rotate(-40deg)}
.card-front .reset-one-btn{top:7px;left:8px}
.card-back  .reset-one-btn{top:7px;left:38px}

/* Card back text */
.card-desc-label{font-size:.62rem;color:var(–rose-light);letter-spacing:.1em;font-weight:600;opacity:.7;margin-bottom:2px;text-transform:uppercase}
.card-desc-text{font-size:.76rem;color:rgba(245,237,216,.85);text-align:center;line-height:1.4;margin-top:4px;
max-height:62px;overflow:hidden;display:-webkit-box;-webkit-line-clamp:4;-webkit-box-orient:vertical}
.val-small{font-size:.72rem;color:rgba(201,168,76,.58);margin-top:6px;direction:ltr}

/* Delete animation */
.card-wrapper.removing{animation:card-out .42s ease forwards}
@keyframes card-out{from{opacity:1;transform:scale(1)}to{opacity:0;transform:scale(.7) rotate(-6deg)}}

/* ══ TV MODE ══ */
body.tv-mode .header{padding:16px 12px 12px}
body.tv-mode .header h1{font-size:clamp(1.1rem,2vw,1.8rem)}
body.tv-mode .header-sub{font-size:.72rem}
body.tv-mode .sparkle-row{font-size:.8rem;gap:8px;margin-bottom:3px}
body.tv-mode .deco-line{width:70px}
body.tv-mode .total-banner{margin-bottom:10px;padding:10px 24px;max-width:92%;gap:18px;border-radius:10px}
body.tv-mode .total-label{font-size:.68rem}
body.tv-mode .total-amount{font-size:clamp(1.2rem,2vw,1.8rem)}
body.tv-mode .cards-count{font-size:.65rem}
body.tv-mode .cards-count span{font-size:1rem}
body.tv-mode .controls{margin-bottom:10px}
body.tv-mode .btn{padding:6px 14px;font-size:.72rem}
body.tv-mode .board{grid-template-columns:repeat(10,1fr)!important;gap:8px;padding:0 10px;max-width:100%}
body.tv-mode .card-wrapper{height:136px}
body.tv-mode .card-face{padding:10px 8px 8px;border-radius:10px}
body.tv-mode .card-num{font-size:.52rem;top:5px;right:7px}
body.tv-mode .card-value-display{font-size:.95rem;margin:2px 0}
body.tv-mode .card-currency{font-size:.55rem;margin-top:2px}
body.tv-mode .gift-icon{font-size:.85rem;margin-bottom:1px}
body.tv-mode .flip-hint{display:none}
body.tv-mode .edit-btn{display:none}
body.tv-mode .reset-one-btn{width:18px;height:18px;font-size:.6rem}
body.tv-mode .card-front .reset-one-btn{top:5px;left:6px}
body.tv-mode .card-back  .reset-one-btn{top:5px;left:29px}
body.tv-mode .delete-btn{width:18px;height:18px;font-size:.6rem;top:5px;left:6px}
body.tv-mode .card-desc-label{font-size:.48rem}
body.tv-mode .card-desc-text{font-size:.52rem;max-height:40px;-webkit-line-clamp:3;margin-top:2px}
body.tv-mode .val-small{font-size:.5rem;margin-top:2px}
body.tv-mode .app{padding-bottom:20px}

/* TV badge */
.tv-badge{display:none;position:fixed;top:12px;left:12px;
background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(–gold-dark),var(–gold));color:#0A0A0F;
font-size:.68rem;font-weight:700;padding:3px 12px;border-radius:20px;
z-index:999;letter-spacing:.06em;box-shadow:0 2px 12px var(–shadow-gold)}
body.tv-mode .tv-badge{display:block}

@media(max-width:600px){
.board{gap:12px;padding:0 12px}
.card-wrapper{height:185px}
.total-banner{flex-direction:column;gap:8px;padding:16px 20px}
}

/* ═══════════ SPLASH ═══════════ */
#splash {
position: fixed;
inset: 0;
z-index: 9999;
cursor: pointer;
display: flex;
align-items: flex-start;
justify-content: center;
overflow: hidden;
user-select: none;
}
.splash-bg {
position: absolute;
inset: 0;
background-size: cover;
background-position: center top;
transform: scale(1.03);
transition: transform 8s ease;
}
#splash:hover .splash-bg { transform: scale(1.07); }
.splash-overlay {
position: absolute;
inset: 0;
background:
linear-gradient(180deg,
rgba(0,0,0,.72) 0%,
rgba(0,0,0,.18) 35%,
rgba(0,0,0,.08) 60%,
rgba(0,0,0,.55) 100%
);
}
.splash-content {
position: relative;
z-index: 2;
text-align: center;
padding: 48px 28px 28px;
width: 100%;
max-width: 860px;
animation: splash-in 1.1s cubic-bezier(.16,1,.3,1) both;
}
@keyframes splash-in {
from { opacity:0; transform:translateY(-28px); }
to   { opacity:1; transform:translateY(0); }
}
.splash-deco {
display: flex;
align-items: center;
justify-content: center;
gap: 16px;
margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.splash-deco-bottom { margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0; }
.sdeco-line {
flex: 1;
max-width: 140px;
height: 1.5px;
background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #C9A84C, transparent);
}
.sdeco-gem {
font-size: 1.1rem;
color: #F0D080;
text-shadow: 0 0 16px rgba(201,168,76,.9);
animation: gem-pulse 2.4s ease-in-out infinite;
}
@keyframes gem-pulse { 0%,100%{opacity:1;transform:scale(1)} 50%{opacity:.65;transform:scale(1.2)} }
.splash-title {
font-family: ‘Frank Ruhl Libre’, serif;
font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 5.5vw, 3.6rem);
font-weight: 900;
line-height: 1.25;
letter-spacing: -.01em;
/* dark visible text with gold shimmer */
color: #F0D080;
text-shadow:
0 2px 0 rgba(0,0,0,.9),
0 0 40px rgba(201,168,76,.6),
0 0 80px rgba(201,168,76,.25);
-webkit-text-stroke: 0.5px rgba(0,0,0,.4);
}
.splash-hint {
margin-top: 32px;
font-family: ‘Heebo’, sans-serif;
font-size: clamp(.9rem, 2vw, 1.2rem);
color: rgba(255,255,255,.7);
letter-spacing: .12em;
animation: hint-bounce .7s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
text-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,.8);
}
@keyframes hint-bounce { from{transform:translateY(0)} to{transform:translateY(-5px)} }

/* click-out animation */
#splash.hiding {
animation: splash-out .65s cubic-bezier(.4,0,1,1) forwards;
pointer-events: none;
}
@keyframes splash-out {
from { opacity:1; transform:scale(1); }
to   { opacity:0; transform:scale(1.04); }
}
/* ════════════════════════════════ */

</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ═══════════════ SPLASH SCREEN ═══════════════ -->

<div id="splash" onclick="enterGame()">

  <div class="splash-bg" style="background-image:url('data:image/jpeg;base64,')"></div>
  <div class="splash-overlay"></div>

  <div class="splash-content">
    <div class="splash-deco">
      <div class="sdeco-line"></div>
      <div class="sdeco-gem">✦</div>
      <div class="sdeco-line"></div>
    </div>
    <h1 class="splash-title">מזל טוב לאמא קרן המדהימה<br>ליום הולדתך ה-50</h1>
    <div class="splash-deco splash-deco-bottom">
      <div class="sdeco-line"></div>
      <div class="sdeco-gem">✦</div>
      <div class="sdeco-line"></div>
    </div>
    <p class="splash-hint">לחצי להתחיל 🎁</p>
  </div>

</div>
<!-- ═════════════════════════════════════════════ -->

<div class="tv-badge">📺 מצב טלוויזיה</div>

<div class="app" id="appRoot">
  <header class="header">
    <div class="sparkle-row">✨ 🌹 🎂 🌹 ✨</div>
    <div class="header-deco">
      <div class="deco-line"></div><div class="deco-diamond"></div><div class="deco-line"></div>
    </div>
    <h1>מזל טוב קרן לביא<br>ליום הולדת 50</h1>
    <p class="header-sub">לחצי על קלף כדי לגלות את המתנה שלך 🎁</p>
  </header>

  <div class="total-banner">
    <div>
      <div class="total-label">סך כל הערך</div>
      <div class="total-amount" id="totalAmount">₪50,000</div>
    </div>
    <div class="cards-count"><span id="cardsCount">50</span>קלפים פעילים</div>
  </div>

  <div class="controls">
    <button class="btn btn-tv" id="btnTV" onclick="toggleTV()">📺 מצב טלוויזיה</button>
    <button class="btn btn-restore" onclick="restoreDeleted()">⟳ החזר קלפים מחוקים</button>
    <button class="btn btn-reset-all" onclick="resetAllCards()">↺ איפוס הכל</button>
  </div>

  <div class="board" id="board"></div>
</div>

<script>
var DEFAULTS=[
  {value:2000,desc:"חופשה רומנטית לזוגות בסופ\"ש — כולל לינה ועיסוי מפנק"},
  {value:800, desc:"ספא מפנק ליום שלם — מסאז', ג'קוזי ופינוקים"},
  {value:1500,desc:"ארוחה גורמה לשניים במסעדה עם כוכב מישלן"},
  {value:500, desc:"קורס בישול עם שף מקצועי — חוויה קולינרית"},
  {value:1200,desc:"שובר לחנות בגדים — בחרי מה שמחייך אותך ✨"},
  {value:700, desc:"ביקור בגלריה + ערב תרבות בעיר"},
  {value:900, desc:"כרטיסים לקונצרט — ערב בלתי נשכח 🎵"},
  {value:600, desc:"חבילת יופי — תספורת, צבע וטיפול פנים"},
  {value:1100,desc:"שיעורי רכיבה על סוסים — חוויה מרגשת 🐴"},
  {value:400, desc:"ספרים ויין — ערב שקט ומפנק לנפש 📚🍷"},
  {value:800, desc:"סיור אוכל ורחובות בעיר עתיקה"},
  {value:2500,desc:"כרטיסי טיסה ליעד הבא ברשימה שלך ✈️"},
  {value:350, desc:"מינוי שנתי לפודקאסט + ספרי שמע"},
  {value:650, desc:"קורס צילום — לתפוס רגעים יפים 📸"},
  {value:1000,desc:"שובר סוויטה למלון בוטיק מפנק"},

var KEY='keren50_v3';
var cards=[];
var tvMode=false;

function freshCards(){
  return DEFAULTS.map(function(d,i){
    return{id:i,value:d.value,desc:d.desc,flipped:false,deleted:false,seenBack:false,editingFront:false,editingBack:false};
  });
}

function initCards(){
  try{
    var raw=localStorage.getItem(KEY);
    if(raw){
      var p=JSON.parse(raw);
      if(Array.isArray(p)&&p.length===50){cards=p;return;}
    }
  }catch(e){}
  cards=freshCards();
  save();
}

function save(){
  try{localStorage.setItem(KEY,JSON.stringify(cards));}catch(e){}
}

function getActive(){return cards.filter(function(c){return!c.deleted;});}

function updateTotal(){
  var t=getActive().reduce(function(s,c){return s+(Number(c.value)||0);},0);
  var el=document.getElementById('totalAmount');
  el.textContent='₪'+t.toLocaleString('he-IL');
  el.classList.remove('updated');void el.offsetWidth;el.classList.add('updated');
  document.getElementById('cardsCount').textContent=getActive().length;
}

function renderBoard(){
  var b=document.getElementById('board');
  b.innerHTML='';
  getActive().forEach(function(c){b.appendChild(mkCard(c));});
  updateTotal();
}

function rerenderCard(card){
  var ex=document.getElementById('cw-'+card.id);
  if(!ex){renderBoard();return;}
  var fresh=mkCard(card);fresh.style.animationDelay='0s';
  ex.replaceWith(fresh);
  updateTotal();
}

function mkEl(tag,cls){var e=document.createElement(tag);e.className=cls;return e;}
function mkBtn(cls,txt,ttl){var b=document.createElement('button');b.className=cls;b.textContent=txt;if(ttl)b.title=ttl;return b;}

function mkCard(card){
  var w=document.createElement('div');
  w.className='card-wrapper';w.id='cw-'+card.id;
  w.style.animationDelay=(card.id*0.022)+'s';

  var inner=document.createElement('div');
  inner.className='card-inner'+(card.flipped?' flipped':'');
  inner.addEventListener('click',function(e){
    if(e.target.closest('.edit-btn,.delete-btn,.reset-one-btn,.btn-save')||
       e.target.tagName==='INPUT'||e.target.tagName==='TEXTAREA')return;
    doFlip(card.id);
  });

  inner.appendChild(mkFront(card));
  inner.appendChild(mkBack(card));
  w.appendChild(inner);
  return w;
}

function mkFront(card){
  var f=mkEl('div','card-face card-front');
  f.appendChild(function(){var n=mkEl('div','card-num');n.textContent='#'+(card.id+1);return n;}());

  if(!card.editingFront){
    var rb=mkBtn('reset-one-btn','↺','איפוס קלף לערכים המקוריים');
    rb.addEventListener('click',function(e){e.stopPropagation();resetOne(card.id);});
    f.appendChild(rb);

    var gi=mkEl('div','gift-icon');gi.textContent='🎁';f.appendChild(gi);
    var vd=mkEl('div','card-value-display');
    vd.textContent='₪'+Number(card.value).toLocaleString('he-IL');f.appendChild(vd);

    var fh=mkEl('div','flip-hint');fh.textContent='לחץ להפוך';f.appendChild(fh);

    var eb=mkBtn('edit-btn','✎','ערוך ערך');
    eb.addEventListener('click',function(e){e.stopPropagation();card.editingFront=true;save();rerenderCard(card);});
    f.appendChild(eb);
  } else {
    var inp=document.createElement('input');
    inp.className='card-edit-input';inp.type='number';inp.value=card.value;inp.placeholder='סכום ₪';
    inp.addEventListener('click',function(e){e.stopPropagation();});
    var sb=mkBtn('btn-save','✓ שמור',null);
    sb.addEventListener('click',function(e){
      e.stopPropagation();
      var v=parseInt(inp.value);if(!isNaN(v)&&v>=0)card.value=v;
      card.editingFront=false;save();rerenderCard(card);updateTotal();
    });
    f.appendChild(inp);f.appendChild(sb);
  }
  return f;
}

function mkBack(card){
  var f=mkEl('div','card-face card-back');
  f.appendChild(function(){var n=mkEl('div','card-num');n.textContent='#'+(card.id+1);return n;}());

  var db=mkBtn('delete-btn','✕','מחק קלף');
  db.addEventListener('click',function(e){e.stopPropagation();doDelete(card.id);});
  f.appendChild(db);

  var rb=mkBtn('reset-one-btn','↺','איפוס קלף לערכים המקוריים');
  rb.addEventListener('click',function(e){e.stopPropagation();resetOne(card.id);});
  f.appendChild(rb);

  if(!card.editingBack){
    var dl=mkEl('div','card-desc-label');dl.textContent='🎀 המתנה שלך';f.appendChild(dl);
    var dt=mkEl('div','card-desc-text');dt.textContent=card.desc||'לחצי לערוך תיאור';f.appendChild(dt);
    var vs=mkEl('div','val-small');vs.textContent='₪'+Number(card.value).toLocaleString('he-IL');f.appendChild(vs);

    var eb2=mkBtn('edit-btn','✎','ערוך תיאור');
    eb2.style.borderColor='rgba(200,75,110,.3)';
    eb2.addEventListener('click',function(e){e.stopPropagation();card.editingBack=true;save();rerenderCard(card);});
    f.appendChild(eb2);
  } else {
    var ta=document.createElement('textarea');
    ta.className='card-desc-input';ta.value=card.desc;ta.placeholder='תיאור המתנה...';
    ta.addEventListener('click',function(e){e.stopPropagation();});
    var sb2=mkBtn('btn-save btn-save-back','✓ שמור',null);
    sb2.addEventListener('click',function(e){
      e.stopPropagation();card.desc=ta.value;card.editingBack=false;save();rerenderCard(card);
    });
    f.appendChild(ta);f.appendChild(sb2);
  }
  return f;
}

function doFlip(id){
  var card=cards[id];if(!card||card.deleted)return;
  card.flipped=!card.flipped;
  if(card.flipped)card.seenBack=true;
  save();
  var inner=document.querySelector('#cw-'+id+' .card-inner');
  if(inner) inner.classList.toggle('flipped',card.flipped);
}

function doDelete(id){
  var w=document.getElementById('cw-'+id);if(!w)return;
  w.classList.add('removing');
  setTimeout(function(){
    cards[id].deleted=true;save();w.remove();updateTotal();
  },420);
}

function resetOne(id){
  var orig=DEFAULTS[id];if(!orig)return;
  var wasDeleted=cards[id]&&cards[id].deleted;
  cards[id]={id:id,value:orig.value,desc:orig.desc,flipped:false,deleted:false,seenBack:false,editingFront:false,editingBack:false};
  save();
  if(wasDeleted){
    renderBoard();
  } else {
    var ex=document.getElementById('cw-'+id);
    if(ex){var fresh=mkCard(cards[id]);fresh.style.animationDelay='0s';ex.replaceWith(fresh);}
    updateTotal();
  }
}

// Restore all deleted cards — keeps all edits (values, descs, flips), only un-deletes
function restoreDeleted(){
  var deletedCount=cards.filter(function(c){return c.deleted;}).length;
  if(deletedCount===0){alert('אין קלפים מחוקים — כל 50 הקלפים כבר מוצגים בלוח!');return;}
  cards.forEach(function(c){c.deleted=false;});
  save();
  renderBoard();
}

function resetAllCards(){
  if(!confirm('לאפס את כל 50 הקלפים לערכים המקוריים?'))return;
  localStorage.removeItem(KEY);
  cards=freshCards();
  save();
  renderBoard();
}

function toggleTV(){
  tvMode=!tvMode;
  document.body.classList.toggle('tv-mode',tvMode);
  var btn=document.getElementById('btnTV');
  if(tvMode){
    btn.textContent='✕ צא ממצב טלוויזיה';
    btn.style.cssText='background:linear-gradient(135deg,#7B1F40,#C84B6E);color:#fff;box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(200,75,110,.4)';
    var el=document.documentElement;
    if(el.requestFullscreen)el.requestFullscreen();
    else if(el.webkitRequestFullscreen)el.webkitRequestFullscreen();
  } else {
    btn.textContent='📺 מצב טלוויזיה';
    btn.style.cssText='';
    if(document.exitFullscreen)document.exitFullscreen();
    else if(document.webkitExitFullscreen)document.webkitExitFullscreen();
  }
}

document.addEventListener('fullscreenchange',function(){
  if(!document.fullscreenElement&&tvMode){
    tvMode=false;document.body.classList.remove('tv-mode');
    var btn=document.getElementById('btnTV');btn.textContent='📺 מצב טלוויזיה';btn.style.cssText='';
  }
});
document.addEventListener('webkitfullscreenchange',function(){
  if(!document.webkitFullscreenElement&&tvMode){
    tvMode=false;document.body.classList.remove('tv-mode');
    var btn=document.getElementById('btnTV');btn.textContent='📺 מצב טלוויזיה';btn.style.cssText='';
  }
});


function enterGame() {
  var s = document.getElementById('splash');
  s.classList.add('hiding');
  setTimeout(function(){ s.style.display = 'none'; }, 650);
}

initCards();
renderBoard();
</script>

</body>
</html>
